{"text_id":24368,"tokens":["##"," The"," Crucial"," Responsibility"," to"," Prior","itize"," Safety",":"," Phone"," Use"," and"," Driving","\n\n","The"," proliferation"," of"," smartphones"," has"," brought"," a"," constant"," source"," of"," connectivity",","," but"," its"," ubiquitous"," presence"," poses"," a"," significant"," threat"," to"," road"," safety","."," While"," there"," is"," a"," place"," for"," responsible"," phone"," usage"," in"," our"," daily"," lives",","," it"," is"," imperative"," to"," prioritize"," safety"," by"," preventing"," phone"," use"," while"," driving","."," The"," potential"," consequences"," of"," such"," negligence"," extend"," far"," beyond"," a"," momentary"," inconvenience",","," affecting"," both"," individual"," drivers"," and"," the"," wider"," community",".","\n\n","Appropriate"," use"," of"," phones"," includes"," situations"," where"," hands","-","free"," options"," are"," available",","," such"," as"," when"," planning"," a"," route"," or"," listening"," to"," hands","-","free"," entertainment","."," Additionally",","," public"," spaces"," designed"," for"," socializing"," or"," leisurely"," communication"," are"," suitable"," for"," phone"," use","."," However",","," the"," act"," of"," operating"," a"," vehicle"," demands"," our"," complete",","," undivided"," attention",".","\n\n","The"," devastating"," consequences"," of"," distracted"," driving"," are"," well"," documented","."," Studies"," reveal"," that"," texting"," while"," driving"," increases"," the"," risk"," of"," crashes"," by"," four"," times",","," and"," talking"," on"," the"," phone"," hands","-","free"," still"," doubles"," the"," risk","."," Such"," reckless"," behavior"," not"," only"," end","angers"," the"," lives"," of"," drivers",","," but"," also"," innocent"," pedestrians"," and"," other"," road"," users","."," The"," potential"," for"," catastrophic"," outcomes"," mandates"," a"," categorical"," ban"," on"," phone"," use"," while"," driving","